      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and housed in a climate-controlled environment, every surface\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior\u2014exudes refinement. This is an investment-grade example intended for the discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality and documented mechanical excellence.",
