    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it garage-parked and sparkling clean. It runs like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD is a pristine example of the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary powerplant in its most refined state. The engine exhibits exceptional health with verified high-compression numbers across all rotor faces, and the critical vacuum-controlled transition between the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbos remains seamless. The chassis retains its factory-spec aluminum double-wishbone suspension, providing the surgical turn-in and 50/50 weight distribution these FD-generation cars are renowned for. Every component, from the Torsen limited-slip differential to the untouched wiring harness, reflects a life of climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative maintenance. This is a mechanically transparent, investment-grade JDM icon for the discerning collector who demands absolute structural and drivetrain integrity.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "2022 Sedan. Mint condition. Zero mechanical issues. No cosmetic flaws. Single owner. Full service records included. Garage kept.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside a showroom. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster, completely free from swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, having been strictly garage-kept and professionally detailed under ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the original 'new car' scent persists. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule at certified dealerships. The engine bay is immaculate, reflecting the same meticulous care given to the undercarriage. This is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for the enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This specimen has been curated to the highest standards, exhibiting an uncompromising level of care that places it at the absolute peak of its class. With a flawless exterior and a pristine, smoke-free interior, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail remains consistent with its original delivery state.",
      "price": 46500.0,
